  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680340/extras/b77a2537fcf0055ac27a1ea6bfe37dd7.webp?t=1760137462\" width=610 height=32 /></span><br><br>You're playing as a demoness called by lay occultists. During the summoning ritual, they made a mistake and raised the dead, while turning themselves into zombies.<br>Now you have to return home by jumping to other worlds through portals, all while making your way through the hordes of the undead.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What's the game all about?</h2>It's a simple campaign-style, third-person shooter.<br>Shoot zombies and other monsters to move to other worlds. Defeat all the bosses guarding the portals.<br>As you progress through the game, look for new weapons and hidden ammo. Use them sparingly:<br>it's not so easy to beat the undead in combat.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680340/extras/618cc6f6086e457af7637f28759dbafc.poster.avif?t=1760137462\" width=610 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680340/extras/618cc6f6086e457af7637f28759dbafc.webm?t=1760137462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680340/extras/618cc6f6086e457af7637f28759dbafc.mp4?t=1760137462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680340/extras/b77a2537fcf0055ac27a1ea6bfe37dd7.webp?t=1760137462\" width=610 height=32 /></span><br><br>You're playing as a demoness called by lay occultists. During the summoning ritual, they made a mistake and raised the dead, while turning themselves into zombies.<br>Now you have to return home by jumping to other worlds through portals, all while making your way through the hordes of the undead.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What's the game all about?</h2>It's a simple campaign-style, third-person shooter.<br>Shoot zombies and other monsters to move to other worlds. Defeat all the bosses guarding the portals.<br>As you progress through the game, look for new weapons and hidden ammo. Use them sparingly:<br>it's not so easy to beat the undead in combat.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680340/extras/618cc6f6086e457af7637f28759dbafc.poster.avif?t=1760137462\" width=610 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680340/extras/618cc6f6086e457af7637f28759dbafc.webm?t=1760137462\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1680340/extras/618cc6f6086e457af7637f28759dbafc.mp4?t=1760137462\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
